(ALL-UNICODE-MAPPINGS
  [LAMBDA (INVERTED FILE)                                    (* ; "Edited 22-Feb-2026 10:42 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited 24-Apr-2025 15:51 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited 31-Jan-2025 17:46 by rmk")
